%h2 Create a new company account

%p Please do not create a new company account if you believe one already exists.  You must contact us to be added to the existing company account to gain access to the backlogs within that account.

= form_for(@company) do |f|
  - unless @company.errors.blank?
    .form_errors
      The form was not completed correctly.  Please correct the following fields to register:
      %ul
        - @company.errors.full_messages.each do |error|
          %li
            = error
  = f.label :name, "Company name"
  = f.text_field :name
  %br/
  = f.submit "Create new company"
  